We seek $DE$, and we have $EF$ and $\angle D$.  We can relate these three with the tangent function: \[\tan D = \frac{EF}{DE},\]so  \[DE = \frac{EF}{\tan D} = \frac{9}{\tan D} \approx \boxed{19.3}.\]. The answer is 19.3

